  },
  {
    "client_msg_id": "7b6a3dfa-23af-4a44-9280-0c410bc39795",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@UEP7RL0HX> the case for complex apps is that many techniques and ideas that have worked with small programs in the past don't scale.\n\nOn the other hand it's plausible that it doesn't matter for EUP as this channel seems to conceive it.",
